{"tid":1258910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會原定審議用地撥解放軍作碼頭決議　建制提休會辯論","createTime":"2019-06-26T10:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T11:03:49.000Z","uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"471a277f904c06349981bcd1f732206d62cc1a1c","tid":1258910,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"立會原定審議用地撥解放軍作碼頭決議　建制提休會辯論<br />\n<br />\n立法會原訂即將審議將中環海濱部分用地，撥給解放軍作軍事碼頭的決議案。有建制派議員於審議前，提出休會辯論，討論目前社會形勢。立法會主席梁君彥接納休會辯論的建議，意味立法會不會討論有關決議案，決議案將會於星期六自動生效。<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-26 18:24:43<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自動生效？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be6f8f80ce4c91433500f3d9fe551f7081b77fc","tid":1258910,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75dcb770bb1ba131cb3672c781b8859a4058e30","tid":1258910,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"白票保皇派大成功<br />\n見識到未？後悔未？<br />\n我一早話白票撚有目的<br />\n依加呢班人成功左就潛晒水"},{"pid":"957df0394efeb75743f06e3f0f81830bc12d0e45","tid":1258910,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"原來傾唔掂就可以休會辯論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b330e05d9b6aca09c5492026bb5d9c55590420","tid":1258910,"uid":127553,"like